-- Spain's BBVA to take charge in Q4 from digital investment
-- By Sarah White and Jesus Aguado
-- Wed Oct 29, 2014 04:54AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, Oct 29 (Reuters) - Spain's BBVA <BBVA.MC> said on Wednesday its investment in improving its digital banking offering could hit profits by between 270 million and 290 million euros (369 million US dollar) in the fourth quarter.

